title: Faith Nathan
text:
Faith Nathan (born 27 July 2000) is an Australian <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player.
Career.
She was named in the <a href="Rugby%20sevens%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20team%20squads">Australia squad</a> for the <a href="Rugby%20sevens%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics">Rugby sevens at the 2020 Summer Olympics</a>.
